PART 4: MEASUREMENT INSTRUMENTS & DATA COLLECTION

TIMELINE:

Baseline (T-30 days):
- Environmental assessment (water quality, biodiversity, waste accumulation)
- Unemployment rate and welfare costs
- Community health survey (PSS, ProQOL, purpose scales)
- Institutional trust assessment
- AI displacement risk analysis

Month 3 (Early indicators):
- White Level participation tracking
- Initial income earned
- PSS reduction (early stress relief)
- Water quality preliminary improvement

Month 6 (Mid-point):
- Blue/Green Level progression
- Partnership health assessment
- Environmental data update
- Employment and income tracking

Month 12 (Full cycle):
- All levels operational
- Complete environmental assessment
- Full neurochemical proxy battery
- Partnership sustainability evaluation
- Economic data comprehensive

Year 2-3 (Sustainability):
- Continued employment tracking
- Environmental improvement trajectory
- Gen 2 effects emerging (children's baseline improving)
- Entrepreneurial tier development

---

DATA COLLECTION TEMPLATES:

CSV Format (for importing to Excel/Sheets/database):

# community_baseline.csv
community_id,population,env_cost,unemp_cost,trauma_cost,ai_cost,inst_cost,baseline_date

# participants.csv
participant_id,community_id,ccgb_level,start_date,gender,age_group

# environmental_metrics.csv
community_id,date,water_quality_index,waste_tons_removed,biodiversity_count,soil_health_score,hectares_restored

# economic_metrics.csv
participant_id,date,income_earned,ccgb_level,hours_worked,welfare_exit_flag,business_formed_flag

# neurochemical_proxy.csv
participant_id,date,pss_score,proqol_cs,proqol_bo,proqol_sts,purpose_score,belonging_score

# partnership_health.csv
community_id,date,fn_satisfaction,church_engagement,govt_support,trust_index,conflicts_resolved

# ai_integration.csv
community_id,date,gtt_responses,ai_partner_quality,tech_anxiety_score,work_security_score

# generational_tracking.csv
community_id,date,elder_teaching_hrs,youth_engagement_n,children_attachment_score,baseline_improvement

# multiplier_effects.csv
community_id,date,businesses_formed,equipment_activated,media_value,knowledge_transfers,innovations

